hackathon-description-text: At hackathons, you have the ability to build on any idea you can come up with. Web design, frontend/backend development, iOS and Android apps, hardware hacks, and server management are just a few of the possibilities!

hackathon-prizes.prize-content: Choose from a prize pool of Nintendo Switches, Google Homes, and a mystery item, plus $500 DigitalOcean credit to each hacker.

hackathon-judging-criteria.judging-criterion: Overall design and presentation of the final product. Expo performance and style both fall into this category.
How challenging is the product on a technical level?
How original is the product? Did the team go out of their way to make their project unique?
Did this team go above and beyond? If there was an opportunity to expand on the project did the team take it?
How finished is the product? Is there a complete and functioning demo?
